               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>United Kingdom Ministry of Defence (the “Authority”) intends to place a contract with BAE Systems Surface Ships Limited (company number 06160534) (the “Company”) for In-Service Support for Ships Sensors and Monitoring Systems (SSAMS) equipment fitted to the Royal Navy’s Type 45 Destroyers and Queen Elizabeth Class Carriers.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <DIRECTIVE_2009_81_EC>
                  <AC_CRITERIA>
                     <AC_CRITERION>Criterion 1</AC_CRITERION>
